The setup for the server assumes familiarity with Linux.
A Vagrantfile has been provided for you that takes care of setting up all the dependencies.

To run the server, execute `node server.js` in a terminal from the root of the project folder.


For manual setup


Linux (Ubuntu 14)

1. Setup git

```
sudo apt-get install -y git-core
```

2. Setup nodejs (atleast v7)

3. Set up `graphicsmagick` and `imagemagick` packages

```
sudo add-apt-repository ppa:rwky/graphicsmagick
sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get install graphicsmagick imagemagick -y
```


For mac

brew install imagemagick
brew install graphicsmagick
brew install npm
npm install gm


